{"id":232954874,"title":"Canon FD 50mm f/1.4 老鏡轉接 NIKON Z7 無反","content":"Canon FD 50mm f/1.4 人像定焦老鏡（古董機械相機 Canon AE-1 的 Kit）\n\n【測試】\n1.將老鏡 Canon FD 50mm f/1.4 直接破壞性改裝為 F卡口\n2.免轉接，直上 NIKON DSLR機身\n3.透過 FTZ 只需經一次轉接即可上 NIKON Z系列機身\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/aKKTg0c.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/WVawv0X.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/oN6yIqw.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/cx5QajU.jpg\n\n\n➽ 以下是 FD 50mm f/1.4 無轉接，直上 NIKON DSLR D7000 (APS-C)\nhttp://i.imgur.com/qo8ayFB.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/qtHB9ds.jpg\nAv Mode、50mm(35等效=75mm)、F1.4、1/125、ISO560\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/GR5Oq4h.jpg\nAv Mode、50mm(等效=75mm)、F1.4、1/30、ISO180\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/zo971q4.jpg\nAv Mode、50mm(35等效=75mm)、F1.4、1/125、ISO280\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/gbRbVoy.jpg\nAv Mode、50mm(等效=75mm)、F4.0、1/75、ISO2200\n\n\n➽ 以下為 FD 50mm f/1.4 經 FTZ轉接環，轉接一次至 NIKON Z7 全片幅無反 4575萬畫素\nhttp://i.imgur.com/OEH2v8p.jpg\n\nhttps://photos.app.goo.gl/BWzdkjM5mXsNJ5x26\nAv Mode、50mm、F1.4、1/50、ISO640\n\nhttps://photos.app.goo.gl/LzpZu8RKyKQT6bTn9\nAv Mode、50mm、F2.0、1/50、ISO800\n\nhttps://photos.app.goo.gl/joPkn2KbhRB1ez547\nAv Mode、50mm、F4.0、1/50、ISO2200\n\n先不論成像表現的問題，光是轉接手動老鏡，就碰到一個最大的麻煩，\n早期在 DSLR 數位機身上，可以改裝更換【 裂像對焦屏 】以輔助手動對焦：\nhttp://i.imgur.com/s0to96f.jpg\n\n至於在 Z系列這種無反機身上，則只能開啟機身內【 峰值對焦 】來輔助手動對焦，峰值對焦非常不易察覺，只比 DSLR 出廠的「磨砂對焦屏」好一點點，考驗眼力。。","excerpt":"Canon FD 50mm f/1.4 人像定焦老鏡（古董機械相機 Canon AE-1 的 Kit），【測試】1.將老鏡 Canon FD 50mm f/1.4 直接破壞性改裝為 F卡口，2.免轉接","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T08:50:43.446Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T09:56:48.170Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["手動鏡","老鏡","轉接環","單眼","底片"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"義守大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false